    "name": "好饿的谜姆",
    "steam_appid": 3051240,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >某天，你发现一本绘本，里面讲述了在世界树脚下生活的贪吃生物——“谜姆”的故事。然而，故事的结局非常悲伤……</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你可以影响绘本的内容，为“谜姆”提供“帮助”。和“谜姆”一起努力，为故事创造圆满结局吧！</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>来帮助谜姆吧！</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >“谜姆”在世界树脚下生活，是一种有点贪吃的可爱生物。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >有一天，任何食物都可以美味烹饪的“奇迹大锅”坏了，谜姆面临灭亡危机！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >“帮助”幸存的谜姆，这次一定要创造出生机勃勃的谜姆世界！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3051240/extras/74da68a3e291f0e4fcbabe580ded2c49.poster.avif?t=1753944686\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3051240/extras/74da68a3e291f0e4fcbabe580ded2c49.webm?t=1753944686\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3051240/extras/74da68a3e291f0e4fcbabe580ded2c49.mp4?t=1753944686\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>谜姆是什么？</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >谜姆是一种爱吃、爱睡、爱玩耍的生物。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >积累各种经验，他们就能学会新技能，变成别的模样。让谜姆互相结为伴侣，可以孕育出数之不尽的新种类。积极寻找自己喜欢的谜姆吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3051240/extras/271fad0a90ddf4055d19a62b8a3fb156.poster.avif?t=1753944686\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3051240/extras/271fad0a90ddf4055d19a62b8a3fb156.webm?t=1753944686\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3051240/extras/271fad0a90ddf4055d19a62b8a3fb156.mp4?t=1753944686\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>培育世界树</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >谜姆举办“飨宴”，享用特殊美食，就会散发出喜悦之光，促进世界树成长。随着世界树成长，你便可以跟谜姆一起去更多地方探索，探险的范围也会扩大。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3051240/extras/b298fe556c5bd9e517af772f2fd27ee8.poster.avif?t=1753944686\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3051240/extras/b298fe556c5bd9e517af772f2fd27ee8.webm?t=1753944686\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3051240/extras/b298fe556c5bd9e517af772f2fd27ee8.mp4?t=1753944686\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>让谜姆生活得更好</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在谜姆生活的基地，可以建造“谜姆之家”“爱的小窝”，以及各种资源设施、农业设施和观赏设施。充分使用探索时获取的建材，帮助谜姆过上幸福美满的生活吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3051240/extras/a21ddb2705d5f3e093ba2e6deeef6044.poster.avif?t=1753944686\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3051240/extras/a21ddb2705d5f3e093ba2e6deeef6044.webm?t=1753944686\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3051240/extras/a21ddb2705d5f3e093ba2e6deeef6044.mp4?t=1753944686\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
